description:
Season Six Match
HOLLIE STEVENS
The Amazon
HT: 5'7
WT: 145 lbs
Season record (1-1)
Lifetime record (5-6)
Ranked 9th
AMI EMERSON
The Valkyrie
HT: 5'7
WT: 130lbs
Season record (0-1)
Lifetime record (0-1)
Ranked 8th
A great battle between two similarly ranked opponents. 8th vs 9th - who wants it more!
Hollie is currently ranked 9th and does not like the fact that the newcomer who has only wrestled once is ranked above her. She is determined to put the rookie in her place.
With one loss to Vendetta, Ami Emerson looked good - good enough to be ranked 8th. Was that a mistake? Is she really that good after only one match?
title: Hollie Stevens "The Amazon" (1-1)
